Ambitious – bahut zyada safalta paane ki ichha
(Example: She is very ambitious about her career.)
Confident – atmavishwas se bhara hua
(He speaks confidently in public.)
Opportunity – mauka
(This job is a great opportunity.)
Challenge – chunauti
(Learning English can be a challenge.)
Improve – sudhaar karna
(I want to improve my English.)
Achieve – hasil karna / praapt karna
(She achieved her goals.)
Knowledge – gyaan
(Reading increases knowledge.)
Communicate – baat-cheet karna
(We need to communicate clearly.)
Effective – prabhavi
(This method is very effective.)
Develop – vikas karna
(Try to develop new skills.)
